<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us – Sweet Layers Bakery</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">Sweet Layers</div>
    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger">&#9776;</button>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/menu">Menu</a></li>
      <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>A little story about the people behind every bake.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR STORY -->
  <section class="about-story">
    <div class="about-story-inner">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Sweet Layers started in a small kitchen in Lahore in 2015. What began as a weekend hobby — baking cakes for family and friends — quickly turned into something much bigger when word spread around the neighbourhood.</p>
        <p>We use fresh, natural ingredients and family recipes passed down through generations. No preservatives, no shortcuts, no artificial colours — just honest, good baking made with care and patience.</p>
        <p>Today we bake hundreds of orders every month, but every cake still gets the same personal attention it did on day one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <h3>10+</h3>
          <p>Years of Baking</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <h3>5,000+</h3>
          <p>Happy Customers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <h3>100%</h3>
          <p>Natural Ingredients</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <h3>0</h3>
          <p>Preservatives Used</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR VALUES -->
  <section class="values">
    <h2>What We Believe In</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌿</div>
        <h3>Fresh Ingredients Only</h3>
        <p>We source local, seasonal ingredients. If it's not fresh, it doesn't go into our cakes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">👩‍🍳</div>
        <h3>Baked to Order</h3>
        <p>Nothing sits on a shelf. Every order is baked fresh the day it's picked up or delivered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
        <h3>Attention to Detail</h3>
        <p>From the sponge to the final decoration, every layer gets the care it deserves.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <h2>Want to Try Our Bakes?</h2>
    <p>Browse our menu or get in touch to place a custom order.</p>
    <a href="/menu" class="btn btn-light">See Our Menu</a>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Sweet Layers Bakery. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
